


How to Create your Own Cocoapods
There is few basic commands which generally uses.

//============================ Command =====================

sudo gem install cocoapods
pod —version

 pod lib create YouProjectName 


cd YouProjectName  "Navigate to the root folder of your project"

YourProjectPath : git init

YourProjectPath:  git add -A

YourProjectPath : git commit  —m  "Initial commit with cocoa pods  template"

YourProjectPath : git remote add origin  urlHere

#”Replace with your remote URL"

YourProjectPath :  git push —u origin master

YourProjectPath : pod trunk register 'Your email ID'

YourProjectPath : pod lib lint  YourProjectName.podspec

YourProjectPath : pod trunk push YourProjectName.podspec

YourProjectPath  :  pod install

YourProjectPath : pod update
